# ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ Generated benchmark outputs ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
# The canonical projection data is committed as benchmark.json at the repo
# root. Runtime outputs from `make check` and the benchmark adapters should
# NOT be committed ‚Äî they are user-specific.
results.json
results_*.json
benchmarks/*/results_*.json
benchmarks/*/data/

# ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ LibreOffice lock files (in case docs are edited locally) ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
.~lock.*#

# ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ Temporary files ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
*.tmp
